<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-11-17T10:15:00-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-11-17T10:15:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T10:15:00-05:00</updated><title> 《君主：怪物的遗产》的创作者不仅仅是想制作一部哥斯拉衍生剧</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个巨大的类似恐龙的生物从雾墙中咆哮。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7uRSJgQleIHn9Dzkf-9hFPUQzZs=/0x0:2199x1466/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875762/Monarch_Legacy_of_Monsters_Photo_010104 .0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Monarch 联合创作者 Chris Black 和 Matt Fraction 以及导演 Matt Shakman 讲述了为什么他们的新 MonsterVerse 系列如此关注普通人类。&lt;/p >; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23960969/monarch-legacy-of-monsters-matt-shakman-matt-fraction-chris-black-interview&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a >; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23960969/monarch-legacy-of-monsters-matt-shakman-matt-fraction-chris-black-interview" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23960969/monarch-legacy-of-monsters-matt-shakman-matt-fraction-chris-black-interview</id><author><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T10:01:54-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T10:01:54-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 为妈妈们准备的 2023 年节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/L6N2nmWpZ-tCeYFFnr6LkNtS70I=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875697/236830_FOR_MOMS_Gift_Guide_ Artboards_CVirginia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;一系列炫酷、平静且富有创意的礼物，以表达您对生活中特殊母亲形象的欣赏.&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23955826/holiday-gifts-mom-unique-ideas-2023-tech-gadgets&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23955826/holiday-gifts-mom-unique-ideas-2023-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23955826/holiday-gifts-mom-unique-ideas-2023-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T09:46:20-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T09:46:20-05:00</updated><title>这是一款让你过上低调生活的键盘</title><content type="html">&lt;p>;Lofree Flow 是一款低调的键盘，打字和听起来都像全高键盘。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965283/lofree-flow -low-profile-keyboard-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23965283/lofree-flow-low-profile-keyboard-review" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965283/lofree-flow-low-profile-keyboard-review</id><author><name>丹·塞弗特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</updated><title>凯迪拉克新款 Optiq 紧凑型电动 SUV 将是最便宜的电动汽车</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;橙色凯迪拉克 SUV，顶部涂成黑色，位于玻璃面板建筑前&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4ZB7B8Q9Mqb1FQO3FCZZADJjXNE=/0x0:6325x4217/1310x873/cdn .vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875439/MY24_CADILLAC_OPTIQ_SPORT_GMCA0740.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Optiq，你到底有多便宜？&lt;/em>; |图片：凯迪拉克&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;X2AwUB&quot;>;凯迪拉克宣布推出一款名为 Optiq 的新型电动汽车，据称该车型将“作为该汽车制造商在美国的电动汽车产品线的切入点”。此前，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23522467/cadillac-lyriq-ev-review-specs-photos-price&quot;>;售价 64,000 美元的凯迪拉克 Lyriq&lt;/a>; 是该汽车制造商最便宜的电动汽车选择，因此 Optiq 的起价可能会低于 60,000 美元，尽管该公司尚未公布这方面的任何细节。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;EZnEfP&quot;>;事实上，凯迪拉克尚未提供任何细节无论如何，包括关键规格，如电池范围、尺寸、动力系统选项，如是否具有 AWD 标准、充电速度等。尽管未经证实，Optiq 很可能基于通用汽车的 Ultium 电动汽车平台构建。我们所知道的是它至少会采用橙色，具有正面设计......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964593 /cadillac-optiq-ev-compact-suv-teaser&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964593/cadillac-optiq-ev-compact-suv-teaser" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964593/cadillac-optiq-ev-compact-suv-teaser</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</updated><title> Tumblr 在变小上下了大赌注</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;粉色和紫色背景上的 Tumblr 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/V9s3NWknMlUhre6uynnq28E1DjU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn. com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875398/STK137_Tumblr_K_Radtke_01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：边缘&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;社交网络未能实现其新所有者设定的增长目标2019 年。但它们是否与 Tumblr 最擅长的领域兼容？&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964580/tumblr-downscaling-smaller-social -media-site&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964580/tumblr-downscaling-smaller-social-media-site" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964580/tumblr-downscaling-smaller-social-media-site</id><author><name>阿莱格拉·罗森伯格</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</updated><title>亚马逊设备上黑色星期五早期最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;桌子上有一个紫色的 Echo Pop 智能音箱，周围环绕着 Ring Pop 糖果。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ST7cEe9-ENgx3UPQ3QPeAxAp9c8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875400/236685_Amazon_Echo_Pop_JTuohy_0 001.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;亚马逊奇特的 Echo Pop 是一份不错的经济实惠的礼物......尤其是当它的售价低于 20 美元时。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Jennifer Pattison Tuohy / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;nkySMF&quot;>;亚马逊再次对自家设备进行大促销，这似乎是今年第十亿次。然而，这一次是为了纪念&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939216/black-friday-guide-cyber-monday-tech-gadgets-2023&quot;>;黑色星期五&lt;/a>;，尽管大型购物活动要到 11 月 24 日才会真正举行。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;iNWzPb&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem -component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2023 年节日礼物指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 100 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge. com/23951136/gifts-under-100-best-cheap-tech-ideas-2023-budget&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 50 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www. theverge.com/23952179/tech-gifts-under-50-best-cheap-ideas-2023-budget&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;RX3Qyj&quot;>;不我们正在抱怨。毕竟，我们上次在亚马逊最近的 Prime Day 活动期间看到的许多出色优惠又回来了，为您提供了另一个节省费用的机会 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/all-new-amazon -fire-tv-stick-4k-max/dp/B0BP9SNVH9?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;新款 Amazon Fire TV Stick 4K Max&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href =&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Lavender-Bloom-bundle-TP-Link-Smart/dp/B0CL8HJ3HD?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Echo Pop&lt; /a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Kindle-Scribe-the-first-Kindle-for-reading-writing-journaling-and-sketching/dp/B09BS26B8B?tag=theverge02 -20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Kindle Scribe&lt;/a>; 等技术。在某些情况下，亚马逊甚至提供比 10 月份更大幅度的折扣，百思买、塔吉特和其他零售商也是如此。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ZLzK4e&quot;>;在这里，我们进行了汇总最好的黑色星期五优惠...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23963020/black-friday-2023-amazon-deals-cyber-monday&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23963020/black-friday-2023-amazon-deals-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23963020/black-friday-2023-amazon-deals-cyber-monday</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T08:45:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T08:45:00-05:00</updated><title>轮胎拯救了我们，也杀死了我们</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;概念图显示草从轮胎的打滑痕迹中生长出来，旨在展示未来拥有丰富的可持续制造轮胎的可能性。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ThRa1cxlGgEtduIhQ6q6-iREisk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72871431/236801_Sustainable_Tires_Nico_Brausch.0 .jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Nico H. Brausch 为 The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;可持续轮胎正在成为现实，但它们来得足够快吗？ &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23951181/tires-sustainable-rubber-bridgestone-michelin&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23951181/tires-sustainable-rubber-bridgestone-michelin" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23951181/tires-sustainable-rubber-bridgestone-michelin</id><author><name>蒂姆·史蒂文斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T08:15:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T08:15:00-05:00</updated><title>隐藏在智能家居设备中的秘密环境成本</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;概念图显示了大型服务器机房走廊上的一个家。服务器散发出的薄雾暗示着拥有智能家居的环境足迹。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/i4_-hNKB_BlCDnrvO564hMmIU-I=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72871430/236801_Dirty_AI_Nico_Brausch.0。 jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Nico H. Brausch 为 The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;人工智能可能成为导致地球变暖的排放的主要来源。智能家居行业如何打造更可持续的产品？&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23951196/smart-home-ai-data-electricity -fossil-fuel-climate-change&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23951196/smart-home-ai-data-electricity-fossil-fuel-climate-change" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23951196/smart-home-ai-data-electricity-fossil-fuel-climate-change</id><author><name>叶塞尼娅·富内斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T05:47:09-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T05:47:09-05:00</updated><title> Discord 正在关闭其人工智能聊天机器人 Clyde</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Discord 徽标插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/PjjcyNz3po95lPcUSFhbT9bcQZ8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image /image/72874888/acastro_STK062_01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;zWMIXS&quot;>;Discord 正在关闭其实验性 AI 聊天机器人 Clyde。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://support.discord.com/hc/en-us/articles/13066317497239-Clyde-Discord-s-AI-Chatbot&quot;>;支持说明&lt;/a>;中，Discord 表示聊天机器人将将于本月底“停用”，到 12 月 1 日，“用户将无法再在 DM、群组 DM 或服务器聊天中调用 Clyde。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;GcAu7C&quot;>;先Discord今年早些时候开始测试 Clyde 的 AI 功能，使用 OpenAI 的模型让聊天机器人回答问题并与 Discord 用户进行对话。从那时起，它就一直在进行有限的测试，该公司计划将其作为其聊天和社区应用程序的基本组成部分。 &lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：Discord&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Clyde AI 聊天机器人。&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id =&quot;es6baL&quot;>;目前尚不清楚克莱德为何突然关闭。聊天机器人可能会作为付费 Nitro 功能返回...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965185/discord-is- shutdown-its-ai-chatbot-clyde&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965185/discord-is-shutting-down-its-ai-chatbot-clyde" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965185/discord-is-shutting-down-its-ai-chatbot-clyde</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T04:36:14-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T04:36:14-05:00</updated><title> Bellroy 的 iPhone 15 Pro 手机壳现在有一个合适的操作按钮</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示操作和音量按钮的外壳侧面特写。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4fxWt7sfz0xoEkcq3Vo1de_Lo3g=/0x0:3200x2133/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72874846/bellroy_pcxi_terracotta_print_04.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;用传统按钮代替切口。&lt;/em>; |图片：Bellroy&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;080fcy&quot;>;苹果决定在 iPhone 15 Pro 系列上用操作按钮取代静音开关，一些手机壳制造商措手不及，两个月后，Bellroy 做出了回应发布了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fbellroy.com%2Fproducts%2Fphone-case%3Fcolor%3Dblack%26material%3Dleather %26size%3Di15promax%23slide-0&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F11%2F17%2F23965171%2Fbellroy-iphone-15-pro-case-action-button -cutout&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;已更新&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A% 2F%2Fbellroy.com%2Fproducts%2Fphone-case-3-card%3Fcolor%3Deverglade%26material%3Dleather%26size%3Di15promax%23slide-0&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge。 com%2F2023%2F11%2F17%2F23965171%2Fbellroy-iphone-15-pro-case-action-button-cutout&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;范围&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot; https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fbellroy.com%2Fproducts%2Fmod-phone-case-wallet%3Fcolor%3Dterracotta%26material%3Dleather%26size% 3Di15promax%23slide-0&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F11%2F17%2F23965171%2Fbellroy-iphone-15-pro-case-action-button-cutout&quot; rel =“赞助的nofollow noopener”target =“_blank”>;案例&lt;/a>;。与第一次运行时的操作按钮上有一个切口，可能会使其难以伸手按下，新设计有一个更标准的集成按钮。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;pVlaLz&quot;>;“新设计外壳上还包括另一个按钮，可提供与实际设备相同的功能和体验。这更加自然和无缝，”Bellroy 的产品开发主管 Arya Ghavifekr 说道。贝尔罗伊表示，任何购买了第一批带有切口的箱子的人都可以将其换成新型号。它继续销售旧手机壳...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965171/bellroy-iphone-15-pro-case -action-button-cutout&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965171/bellroy-iphone-15-pro-case-action-button-cutout" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965171/bellroy-iphone-15-pro-case-action-button-cutout</id><author><name>乔恩·波特</name></author></entry></feed>